I have been following both teams closely this year and actually hoped for this matchup in the Superbowl. I had Aaron Rogers as my fantasy QB and he delivered this season.  I love Steelers Defense though led by 92 and 43!!!  Either way I expect some pretty great plays on D from both teams.
